= AI, Bounded and Useful
Agentic AI coding assistance was adopted with top-tier models (i.e. Claude 4.5) exceling at coding tasks, delivered via Amazon Q
Developer#link("ref1", super[[1]]). The goal: increase engineering productivity and flow.

#bar-chart(
  (2, 10, 13, 9, 2),
  [Figure 1: Task complexity solved with AI],
  [Scale: 1 = very simple, 5 = very complex],
)
#v(2mm)

Survey results make the value clear: AI helps with medium-complex tasks, developer experience ratings sit near the top of the scale, and teams now delegate to AI  a significant amount of their daily tasks.

#bar-chart(
  (1, 3, 5, 15, 12),
  [Figure 2: AI assistant code contribution and delegation],
  [Scale: 1 = none, 5 = most of the task],
)
We adopted the latest industry AI patterns while keeping engineering judgment in the loop, and addressing AI-era security risks with a secure rollout for engineers.
#v(2mm)
#bar-chart(
